Title : Pravin H. Parekh
Text : {{Use dmy dates|date=July 2019}}
'''Pravin H Parekh''' is a [[senior counsel]] practising at [[Supreme Court of India]]. He has served at six times as the president of the [[Supreme Court Bar Association of India]].  In 2012, Parekh was conferred with [[Padma Shri]], the fourth highest Indian civilian honour.<ref name=LI1>{{cite news|last=Shrivastava|first=Prachi|title=SCBAâ€™s PH Parekh awarded Padma Shree|url=http://www.legallyindia.com/201202082557/Bar-Bench-Litigation/scbas-ph-parekh-awarded-padma-shree|accessdate=25 April 2014|newspaper=Legally India|date=8 February 2012}}</ref>

